Trocando a porta do Jetty
via linha de comando: package jetty:run -Djetty.port=9999

	     <plugin>
               <groupId>org.eclipse.jetty</groupId>
                <artifactId>jetty-maven-plugin</artifactId>
                <version>9.4.0.v20161208</version>
                <configuration>
                	<httpConnector>
                		<port>9999</port>
                	</httpConnector>
                    <scanIntervalSeconds>10</scanIntervalSeconds>
                </configuration>
            </plugin>

